transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Ji madam.
Executive: Ah ha sir aap aapne helpline pe call kiya tha sir.
Customer: Madam lag gaya hoga wo.
Executive: Ha koi issue chal raha hai sir?
Customer: Madam ek to issue ye chal raha hai ki jo meri website bani hui hai SS metal.
Executive: Ha.
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Ispe jo card laga hua hai visiting card jo laga hua hai mera.
Executive: Kya laga hua hai?
Customer: Office card jo laga hua hai mera.
Executive: Sorry aapki aawaz kat gayi sir kya bol rahe hai?
Customer: Office card jo laga hua hai.
Executive: Ha.
Customer: Wo mere ko change karwana tha.
Executive: Okay.
Executive: Aur bhi kuch change karwana hai?
Customer: Nahi ye nahi karwana aap mujhe whatsapp karoge ek bar.
Executive: Ha ek ha ek second rukiye.
Executive: Main to aapko kal bhi call bhi kiya tha.
Executive: Dekho maine abhi aapko message kiya hai.
Customer: Okay.
Executive: Ha aapko maine video meet ka link bhi pichle month to bheja tha but aap connect kar nahi paye the.
Executive: Agar bolo abhi connect kare kya?
Customer: Main thoda main busy chal raha tha isme ek issue aa raha tha wo maine personal tha to wo main aapko batana chahta tha.
Executive: Okay.
Executive: Ha bataiye.

Customer: Aap kuch whatsapp pe bhej rahe ho kya?
Customer: Haan ji haan ji.
Executive: Achcha okay.


Executive: Okay visiting card.

Customer: Ye visiting card hai na?
Customer: Haan ji haan ji.
Executive: Ha to isko visiting card ko change karna hai.
Customer: Haan ji haan ji.
Executive: Okay theek hai change ho jayega iska aapka ye pehla wala black colour ka tha SS metals ka.
Customer: Haan ji haan ji.
Executive: Haan ji haan ji.
Executive: Haan to isko ha ye to aapne front front wala bheja na isko sir acche se click karke aap bhej paoge?
Customer: Chaliye main aapko na abhi to mere paas nahi hai main aapko bhejta hu theek hai.
Executive: Ha aap isko front aur back jo dono hai na dono ko acche se click karke aap bhejiyeega.
Customer: Front hi milega back mein nahi hai isme.
Executive: Achcha back nahi hai okay theek hai to aap front mujhe bhej ha aap mujhe front bhej do taki hum log isko crop bhi kare na to acche se wo crop ho paye kyunki ye photo thoda sa tedha khicha hua hai.
Customer: Hmm hmm main bhejta hu.
Executive: Theek hai.
Executive: Ha aur koi issue hai sir iske alava?
Customer: Abhi to nahi hai abhi fir main batata hu aapko.
Executive: Okay nahi because sir aapne helpline pe call kiya tha na to concern open ho jata hai to isko main pehle karwa du aap abhi mujhe share kar do main isko upload karke fir aapko update karti hu.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai main aapko dikha bhi dungi aur aapse sir services ka discussion bhi pending chal raha hai to aap kis time video meet pe connect kar paoge sir?

Customer: Friday off rehta hai mera Friday ke Sunday.
Executive: Friday ko.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Friday ko kitne baje kar le?
Customer: 11 baje.
Executive: 11 baje theek hai main Friday ko aapko ek bar call bhi kar lungi pehle aap mujhe ye click karke de do main pehle isko upload kar de rahi hu fir main aapko update karke batati hu theek hai.
Customer: Ha.
Executive: Ha okay sir.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants to change the office card.

- Wants to schedule a video meet.



Resolution:

- Agreed to change the office card.

- Scheduled a video meet for Friday at 11 AM.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will send the front image of card.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- visiting card, change, video meet, services
